data.message: Yo Hi Eminem Slim Marshall your Phenomenal *giggles* you are the best rap artist you might even say your what the doctor ordered lol you are Phenomenal you are so unique your lyrics are spell binding your beats are off the hook i fell in love with your songz from day one never once turned my back on you as your number one fan im hooked on your music whats next EmiNem Slim Marshall  cant wait for some more fresh music from you i know you have a life to lead outside music but i would love to hear some more new stuff not that what i think matters but if theres anything i could say to inspire you i would maybe one day i would write my own song but to be honest like ive said before i wouldnt know what words to use theres just so much i want to say to you live life to the fullest now that your a rap Phenomenal God *giggles* doesnt mean you cant achieve greatness i think you already did lol you have so many fans im sure sometimes you could just take a break and be normal and walk amongst us like an everyday joe you are amazing there's no words in the dictionary to say how much you are awesome you are the nicest rapper around never once have i herd the n word come out of your mouth in your lyrics you are more than just a rapper your a trend starter you have brought new life to the rap industry you are the most unbeliievable sexy funny cool guy of the millinium *giggles* any girl would be lucky  you would make anyone happy evrytime i hear your music my ears orgasm such a afrodeziac your tunes are love always your number one fan me *giggles*
